text.4: Waking up to reading awesome profiles in my twitter feed. Keep them coming! @BlackInCardio  #BLACKINCARDIORollCall #BICRollCall
text.5: Hey @BlackInCardio! I'm an Asst. Professor at @osunursing funded by @theNCI. I do #CBPR interventions aiming to improve health and quality of life among #BlackWomen and #BlackMen with #BreastCancer and/or elevated #CVDRisk.  #BlackInCardioWeek #BLACKINCARDIORollCall #BICRollCall https://t.co/YL57vBErwz
text.6: It's #BlackInCardioWeek !! My research focuses on breast cancer disparities that impact Black women. One of my new areas of interest is #cardiooncology -  the study of cardiac dysfunction that occurs as the result of cancer treatments. #BlackInCardioRollCall
